04:04.605 --> 04:08.589
there's a lot of demonstrators out and stuff. So we 
bargained down to 25 yuan to take me over to my

04:08.770 --> 04:13.795
hotel. What was the name of your hotel again? I was 
at the Kunlun Hotel, which is in the northeast side

04:16.238 --> 04:21.504
of the city. So I got into the cab. And he started 
down one of the main streets of parallels, that

04:24.125 --> 04:36.541
ring road, to get over to where my hotel was. And we 
